OL,3,C'Horrendous': Neighbour describes fire
OL,4,Cthat killed mum and three children
OL,6,FA neighbour has described the
OL,7,F"horrendous" moment he witnessed a
OL,8,Ffire that killed a mother and her
OL,9,Fthree children in Bradford.
OL,11,FHarold Pullan, 82, lives opposite the
OL,12,Fsemi-detached property on Westbury
OL,13,FRoad where a blaze broke out in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of Wednesday.
OL,16,FBryonie Gawith, 29, died at the scene.
OL,17,FHer children, 22-month-old Aubree,
OL,18,FOscar, five, and Denisty, nine, died
OL,19,Fin hospital.
