OL,3,C'Horrendous': Neighbour describes fire
OL,4,Cthat killed mum and three children
OL,6,FMr Pullan, who has lived on the street
OL,7,Fall his life, was woken by the
OL,8,Fincident at 3am. He said: "You don't
OL,9,Fexpect to see it - like to watch it in
OL,10,Freal life when people's lives are in
OL,11,Fdanger. I mean it was just so
OL,12,Fhorrendous."
OL,14,FHe added: "I could have had a heart
OL,15,Fattack when I was watching it. I still
OL,16,Fhaven't settled down.
OL,18,F"You don't expect it, do you,
OL,19,Fsomething like that? It's just so hard
OL,20,Fto see."
