OL,3,C'Horrendous': Neighbour describes fire
OL,4,Cthat killed mum and three children
OL,6,FPolice have described the incident as
OL,7,Fdomestic-related.
OL,9,FA 39-year-old man arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of murder remains in
OL,11,Fhospital in a critical condition.
OL,13,FMr Pullan said the family were
OL,14,F"lovely".
