OL,3,C'Horrendous': Neighbour describes fire
OL,4,Cthat killed mum and three children
OL,6,FHe added: "(Bryonie) was nice, I mean,
OL,7,Fwe just passed pleasantries but the
OL,8,Fkids were lovely, they used to play
OL,9,Fout. I like to see the kids play
OL,10,Fbecause I've lived on this road over
OL,11,F82 years and I like to see other
OL,12,Fchildren coming on after me."
OL,14,FHe paid tribute to pay to the
OL,15,Ffirefighters who responded to the
OL,16,Fincident, saying they were "so brave".
