OL,3,C'Horrendous': Neighbour describes fire
OL,4,Cthat killed mum and three children
OL,6,F"I watched them run in to that house,
OL,7,Ffight their way in and fight their way
OL,8,Fout with all the family and the
OL,9,Ffiremen exhausted on the floor when
OL,10,Fthey came out and one getting injured.
OL,11,FIt was just so horrendous."
OL,13,FA book of condolence has been opened
OL,14,Fat St John the Evangelist Church,
OL,15,Fwhere a remembrance service of
OL,16,Fremembrance has been held on Thursday.
